" Feature List:
" https://github.com/XVimProject/XVim2/blob/master/Documents/FeatureList.md

" MARK: CONFIGURE
set relativenumber

" MARK: Mapping
nnoremap U <C-r>
nnoremap Y y$

" Basic commentary
nmap gcc :xcmenucmd Comment Selection<CR>
vmap gc  :xcmenucmd Comment Selection<CR>

vmap > >gv
vmap < <gv

nmap == :xcmenucmd Re-Indent<CR>
vmap =  :xcmenucmd Re-Indent<CR>

" MARK: Leader
nmap <SPACE>cc :w | make<CR>
nmap <SPACE>cr :w | run<CR>
nmap <SPACE>cu :w | xcmenurun Test<CR>
